OL,5,B"Here he is - Gossi The Dog!   Wh!( `|
OL,6,BThe dog with the knack - the   Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bknack-o-dog!                   Wu ba
OL,8,                                Woqs/a>
OL,9,F"Nintendo has been a little narked by  
OL,10,Frecent statements from Sony relating to
OL,11,Fits PlayStation sales figures.         
OL,13,B"Sony has revealed that 30 million     
OL,14,BPlayStations have been sold worldwide  
OL,15,Bto date. Poor Nintendo has been feeling
OL,16,Bawfully insecure about this figure, and
OL,17,Bfelt the need to point out that the    
OL,18,BPlayStation was released a year earlier
OL,19,Bthan its own Nintendo 64. Frrrrng!"    
