OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"What's this I hear, Father?   Wh!( `|
OL,6,BResident Evil 3 already in the Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bworks? But Resident Evil 2 has Wu ba
OL,8,Byet to be released in Europe!  Woqs/a>
OL,10,F"Of course, the record-breaking success
OL,11,Fof Resident Evil 2 in Japan and America
OL,12,Fmeans that Resident Evil 3 was         
OL,13,Finevitable. According to sources, the  
OL,14,Fgame should be ready for release in    
OL,15,Fjust over a year, and new gameplay     
OL,16,Felements are already in discussion.    
OL,18,B"Jumping? More advanced hand to hand   
OL,19,Bcombat? I think so, yes."              
