OL,4,B                               W zk  "u
OL,5,B"Hooray for everything! I've   Wh!( `|
OL,6,Blong been worried that 3DO's   Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bmost risible of platform       Wu ba
OL,8,Bcharacters, Gex The Gecko, was Woqs/a>
OL,9,Bmaking a comeback. The irritatingly-   
OL,10,Bvoiced green git truly turned my       
OL,11,Bstomach with his incessant quips.      
OL,13,F"Leslie Philips, veteran actor of      
OL,14,FDoctor In The House fame, and his      
OL,15,Fcatchphrase 'Ohh, huhllll-oooh!', has  
OL,16,Fbeen hired to do the voice of Gex for  
OL,17,Fthe European market version of Gex 2.  
OL,18,FIt might not make the game better, but 
OL,19,Fit'll make it more tolerable."         
