OL,5,B"The tedium of the Digitiser   Wh!( `|
OL,6,Bnewsgroup debate continues to  Wz~}|3
OL,7,Bbuild. I've been astonished by Wu ba
OL,8,Bthe level of petty bickering   Woqs/a>
OL,9,Bover the damn thing's name.            
OL,11,F"Then again, what am I to expect from  
OL,12,Fan electronic community entirely       
OL,13,Fpopulated by anal retentives?          
OL,15,B"The cry goes out once more - if you   
